<div class="fusion-post-content-wrapper"><div class="fusion-post-content post-content"><h2 class="blog-shortcode-post-title entry-title"><a href="https://gk.city/2018/02/13/carnaval-en-guaranda/">Pawkar Raymi</a></h2><p class="fusion-single-line-meta">
	
	
			<span class="updated" style="display:none;">
			2018-02-13T16:43:14+00:00		</span>
	
 <span class="vcard"><span class="fn"><a href="https://gk.city/author/pablo-davila/" title="Entradas de Pablo Dávila" rel="author">Pablo Dávila</a></span></span><span class="fusion-inline-sep">|</span><a href="https://gk.city/periodismo-narrativo/" rel="category tag">Placeres</a><span class="fusion-inline-sep">|</span></p><div class="fusion-content-sep"></div><div class="fusion-post-content-container"><!--adinj Ad Injection debug mode on--><div  class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:30px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:30px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1  fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last 1_1"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;'>
			<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">
				<p><span class="fusion-dropcap dropcap" style="color:#000000;">E</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n kichwa, </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pawkar Raymi </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">significa la fiesta del florecimiento. Es una festividad que se celebra en honor a Pacha Kamaq, el dios creador de la Tierra, y que coincide con las fiestas de Carnaval de Guaranda, en la provincia de Bolívar, que duran cerca de un mes.</span></p>
<p>Este ensayo fotográfico retrata el desfile de esta antigua ceremonia religiosa<span style="font-weight: 400;"> que sirve para agradecer y compartir los alimentos que cada año les obsequia la madre tierra. </span></p>
<p><div id="attachment_35931" style="max-width: 970px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-35931 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1-200x133.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1-400x267.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1-600x400.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1-800x533.jpg 800w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda1.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">El diablo huma es considerado el guía de la comunidad, líder y guerrero poseedor de la energía vital de la naturaleza. En este caso lo representa un niño.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_35936" style="max-width: 970px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-35936 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8.jpg" alt="carnaval de Guaranda" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8-200x133.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8-400x267.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8-600x400.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8-800x533.jpg 800w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda8.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">La música es parte esencial del desfile. Escuadras de músicos tocan junto a las comparsas animando la fiesta.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_35938" style="max-width: 650px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-35938 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda9.jpg" alt="carnaval de Guaranda" width="640" height="960" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda9-200x300.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda9-300x450.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda9-400x600.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda9-600x900.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda9.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Los niños son considerados los herederos de Pawkar Raymi.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_35937" style="max-width: 970px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-35937 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10.jpg" alt="carnaval de Guaranda" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10-200x133.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10-300x200.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10-400x267.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10-600x400.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda10.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Las danzas tradicionales mantienen vivas las costumbres de la cultura andina de la provincia de Bolivar.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_35932" style="max-width: 970px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-35932 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2-200x133.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2-400x267.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2-600x400.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda2.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Aunque se fomenta el no uso de la espuma de carnaval en realidad se sigue usando.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_35935" style="max-width: 970px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-35935 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5.jpg" alt="carnaval en Guaranda" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5-200x133.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5-300x200.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5-400x267.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5-600x400.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda5.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Las fiestas de carnaval son celebradas por todas las generaciones.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_35939" style="max-width: 970px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-35939 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7.jpg" alt="carnaval de Guaranda" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7-200x133.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7-300x200.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7-400x267.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7-600x400.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda7.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Los niños participan también en el desfile o como espectadores.</p></div>
<div id="attachment_35934" style="max-width: 970px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-35934 size-full" src="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4.jpg" alt="carnaval en Guaranda" width="960" height="640" srcset="https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4-200x133.jpg 200w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4-400x267.jpg 400w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4-600x400.jpg 600w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://gk.city/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Guaranda4.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /><p class="wp-caption-text">La tarima de autoridades es el punto final de desfile donde las varias comparsas ofrecen tributo.</p></div>
